QID2:
EMA_ALONE - How much of the time in the past 3 hours were you alone?

By “alone” we mean you did not interact with anyone for more than a few minutes, neither in person nor on the phone, text, email, social media, or video calls.

For social media, simply scrolling or viewing posts would be considered "alone", but direct interactions such as messaging would be considered an interaction.

EMA_PPL - How many people have you interacted with in the last 3 hours?

Interactions should last more than a few minutes and can include in person, phone, text, email, social media, or video calls.

In considering social media, please consider only direct interactions such as messaging, not scrolling or viewing posts.
